rsSystemResourcesMIB.name: rsSystemResourcesMIB

revisions.description: First Version which has objects for CPU and Memory utilization.

rsSystemResourcesMIB.contactinfo: Riverstone Networks, Inc 5200 Great America Parkway Santa Clara CA USA 95054 PHONE:+1 408.878.6500 EMAIL: nms-eng@riverstonenet.com WEB: http://www.riverstonenet.com
rsSystemResourcesMIB.description: This module defines a schema to access management information pertaining to system resources on Riverstone Device

rsUtlSamplingRate.name: rsUtlSamplingRate
rsUtlSamplingRate.description: Stats are polled at these number of micro seconds interval

rsUtlCPUTable.name: rsUtlCPUTable
rsUtlCPUTable.description: Summary of CPU statistics. It is assumed that there is only one CPU per line card.

rsUtlCPUEntry.name: rsUtlCPUEntry
rsUtlCPUEntry.description: An entry containing CPU utilization information.

rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Sec.name: rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Sec
rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Sec.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 5 seconds at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'system time'.

rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Sec.name: rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Sec
rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Sec.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 5 seconds at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'user time'.

rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization60Sec.name: rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization60Sec
rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization60Sec.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 60 seconds at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'system time'.

rsUtlCPUUserUtilization60Sec.name: rsUtlCPUUserUtilization60Sec
rsUtlCPUUserUtilization60Sec.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 60 seconds at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'user time'.

rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Min.name: rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Min
rsUtlCPUSystemUtilization5Min.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 5 Min at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'system time'.

rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Min.name: rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Min
rsUtlCPUUserUtilization5Min.description: The CPU utilization expressed as an integer percentage. This is calculated over the last 5 Min. at rsUtlSamplingRate interval as a simple average. This is 'user time'.

rsUtlMemoryEntry.name: rsUtlMemoryEntry
rsUtlMemoryEntry.description: An entry containing Memory utilization information.

rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Sec.name: rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Sec
rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Sec.description: The Memory utilization in terms of active pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 5 seconds, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Sec.name: rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Sec
rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Sec.description: The Memory utilization in terms free pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 5 seconds, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlMemoryActivePages60Sec.name: rsUtlMemoryActivePages60Sec
rsUtlMemoryActivePages60Sec.description: The Memory utilization in terms of active pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 60 seconds, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlMemoryFreePages60Sec.name: rsUtlMemoryFreePages60Sec
rsUtlMemoryFreePages60Sec.description: The Memory utilization in terms of free pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 60 seconds, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Min.name: rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Min
rsUtlMemoryActivePages5Min.description: The Memory utilization in terms of active pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 5 Min, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Min.name: rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Min
rsUtlMemoryFreePages5Min.description: The Memory utilization in terms free pages of size 1024 bytes.This is calculated over the last 5 Min, sampled average at every rsUtlSamplingRate

rsUtlComplianceV1.name: rsUtlComplianceV1
rsUtlComplianceV1.description: The compliance statement for the RIVERSTONE-SYSTEM-RESOURCES-MIB.

rsUtlConfGroupV1.name: rsUtlConfGroupV1
rsUtlConfGroupV1.description: A set of managed objects that make up version 1.0 of the Riverstone Utilization mib.
